<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_205_r1l1">Burggraf <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_205_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd gebetten <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> . vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l3">einen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> rats gen Sulcʒbach ʒu leıhen . auf den ſunntag vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l4">ſand oſwalds tag nehſt etc / Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l5">daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag aber ab ıſt vnd niht fürſıch geet . daʒ eẅr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l6"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> ret ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht bedarff <expan>auſſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l7"><expan>Dank<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l8">dıenſt vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ıp<ex>ſ</ex>a</expan> dıe <expan>pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vınc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l9"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> frawn Elıſabethen von payern geborn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l10">Burggraf <expan>frıdr<ex>ichs</ex></expan> <expan>elıch<ex>er</ex></expan> gemaheln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l12"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> dem vıcʒtum ʒu Amberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l13"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> den von Regenſpurg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l11"><expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> muta<ex>n</ex>dıs </ab>
</div>
</div>
<div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_205" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burggraf <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gebetten
                            <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, uns einen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
                        rats gen Sulczbach zu leihen auf den <app><note><q type="date">sunntag vor sand Oswalds tag nehst</q>04.08.1415</note></app>
                        etc., also tun wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag aber ab ist und niht fürsich
                        geet, daz ewr gnade <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ret zu
                                <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht bedarff
                            <expan>ausschik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wir
                            <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz. Denn wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad
                                <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>
<expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> frawn Elisabethen von Payern geborn,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> burggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ichs,</ex></expan>
<expan>elich<ex>er</ex></expan> gemaheln.<lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
                        dem vicztum zu Amberg.<lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> den von Regenspurg
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> muta<ex>n</ex>dis. </ab>
</div>
